The '''Ithorian Nature Priests'''<ref name="Secrets">''[[Secrets of Tatooine]]''</ref> or '''eco-priests''',<ref name="RPG-Core">''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook]]''</ref> were a group of [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorians]] who had been selected to be allowed to walk within the holy ground of the [[Mother Jungle/Legends|Mother Jungle]] of [[Ithor/Legends|their homeworld]], thus being the Mother's chosen. They drew upon [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] to form a fellowship with the jungle, and they sometimes traveled to and from [[Ithorian Herdship|herd ships]] or other locations around [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]], but eventually, they were required to return to the jungles of Ithor and serve the Mother Jungle.<ref name="Secrets" />

